			Posted on <a href="http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2014/04/29/first-men-in-the-moon-by-deshanley/" title="12:00 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-04-29T12:00:23-07:00" pubdate>April 29, 2014</time></a><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://clockworktwist.com/blog/author/" title="View all posts by " rel="author"></a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

